title: Last call to vote for the Lehigh Valley's best quarterback
text:
By Greg Joyce | For lehighvalleylive.com on October 20, 2015 1:25 PM View/Post Comments 
We've entered the final hours of voting for the Lehigh Valley's best quarterback . 
We nominated 32 quarterbacks for your picking last week and it has turned largely into a Bethlehem battle between Liberty 's Doug Erney and Freedom 's Joe Young . 
Vote in the poll below to make sure your voice is heard before the poll ends Tuesday, Oct. 20 at midnight. 
Please note, the results of this poll have no bearing on end-of-the-season All-Area honors.
